data.text:
I guess this isn't really gossip since it's true...

America's Next Top Model season 1 winner Adrienne Curry is a cast member of the new season of VH1's The Surreal Life. Her housemates are Vern Troyer (aka Mini-Me), rapper Da Brat, former pro wrester Chyna, model Marcus Schenkenberg, Jane Wiedlin from the Go-Go's, and actor Christopher Knight (aka Peter Brady).

The new season begins in January.
